  "text": "Note that the left-hand side depends implicitly on \u03b1, \u03b4 and \u03b7 through the choice of \u03b3 r \u222a \u03b3 c . The bound (2.7) results from a slight extension of the arguments in [CITATION_1] , which we briefly explain. It follows from the proof of Theorem 7 in [CITATION_2] that",
